    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Practical, budget-friendly transportation with solid everyday usefulness and plenty of value for the right buyer. This vehicle is best suited for someone seeking an affordable option they can put to work right away, with honest character and a price that makes ownership accessible. A smart buy for commuters, first-time drivers, or anyone looking for inexpensive, no-nonsense motoring.",
