      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of potential? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest budget-friendly ride that could be a great fit for someone who wants simple transportation or a project to tinker with. A good option for a handy buyer who sees the value in a car that still has life left in it without spending a fortune. Priced to move and worth a look if you want something cheap and straightforward.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget commuter with plenty of upside. This car shows cosmetic wear and age, but the engine starts up, the transmission pulls through the gears, and the chassis still feels usable for someone who wants inexpensive transportation or a hands-on fixer-upper. Good candidate for an enthusiast looking for a practical platform with serviceable mechanical bones. Priced to move and worth a look if you know how to turn a wrench.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap, honest, and ready for the next owner. Runs, drives, and priced to move. Great project or budget beater. First serious buyer takes it.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true underdog with plenty of character, this car is the kind of ride that still knows how to show up and get the job done. It has the seasoned presence of something that\u2019s lived a little, and that\u2019s exactly part of its appeal\u2014an affordable set of wheels for someone who values usefulness, grit, and potential over pretense. Perfect as a starter car, backup commuter, or a hands-on project with personality, it offers a chance to own something dependable in spirit and easy on the wallet.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Reliable transportation at an accessible price, this vehicle is a practical option for buyers seeking value and utility over perfection. It shows its age cosmetically and mechanically, but it remains a straightforward, affordable choice for local driving, a backup vehicle, or a project-minded owner. Offered with transparent representation and priced to make sense for the market, this is an economical way to get behind the wheel without overcommitting.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    }
